      "span_text": "National data sources include the Medical Expenditure Panel Survey (MEPS), while state data include administrative program cost data, the Massachusetts Behavioral Risk Factor Surveillance System, and the Massachusetts hospital reduction estimates of Land, et al [CITATION_1] ."
